snippet.title: Banishers: Ghosts of New Eden - Death to the Dead Trailer | The Game Awards 2023
snippet.description:
"Honor your oath or bring me back. But don't leave me like this."

Will you sacrifice the living to resurrect the love of your life?

Immerse yourself in a compelling and personal narrative within this Action-RPG, where you take on the roles of two skilled ghost hunters and partners facing challenging decisions with profound consequences for both the living and the dead.

Banishers: Ghosts of New Eden will be released on February 13, 2024 on PS5, Xbox Series and PC.

Pre-order now and receive the "Wanderer Set" for free when the game launches: https://store.focus-entmt.com/w/banishersghostsofneweden?utm_campaign=BGONE_TGACGITrailer&utm_medium=description&utm_source=YouTube#shop
